  "description": "This image captures a lush forest scene with a majestic waterfall in the background. Towering trees, primarily evergreens and deciduous trees with new green growth, create a dense, layered canopy. The trunks are varying shades of brown and gray, some covered in moss, adding texture and depth to the foreground. Sunlight filters through the leaves, creating highlights and shadows. In the distance, a large waterfall cascades down a sheer rock face, the mist partially obscuring the cliff. The overall impression is one of natural beauty and tranquility.",
